data.meta_description: The Grand Duchess Olga Alexandrovna Romanova of Russia married Nikolai Alexandrovich Kulikovsky on 16 November 1916, in the Kievo-Vasilievskaya Church on Triokhsviatitelskaya Ulitsa (Three Saints St) in Kiev.Only the officiating priest, Olga's mother the Dowager Empress Marie, Olga's brother-in-law Grand Duke Alexander Mikhailovich Romanov of Russia,two fellow nurses from the hospital in Kiev and four officers of the Akhtyrsky Regiment, of which Olga was honorary colonel, attended.
